description: List webjobs for an app, or a deployment slot.

nextlink.description: Link to next page of resources.

resource_group_name.description: Name of the resource group to which the resource belongs.

slot.description: Name of the deployment slot. If a slot is not specified, the API returns deployments for the production slot.

subscription_id.description: Your Azure subscription ID. This is a GUID-formatted string (e.g. 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000).
